x1360/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3G4uc8__BQHQL0JruJQ24H1KA_M=/0x0:2040x1360/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/kQYw_FZUBvWV3zMYPFiOVfR7eUQ=/0x0:2040x1360/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tBYpyt6bfO1olyn1WboHgcUBbK4=/0x0:2040x1360/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/c9f8qYfFYR0ty_ItJHFfdpIDCW8=/0x0:2040x1360/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tTndkyD8NRnewrhVGX2yLNBNCH4=/0x0:2040x1360/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MSVurMQ_0b-O0-G29B6LhqFzQJk=/0x0:2040x1360/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EP4_RxgKvaAMpwjto5R0vz3mOEM=/0x0:2040x1360/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23385634/ajohnson_220411_5138_0004.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"100vw\"></picture><i>The Moto G Stylus has an approachable stylus feature set.</i>Photo by Allison Johnson / The Verge</p><h2>5. MOTOROLA MOTO G STYLUS (2022)</h2><h3>THE BEST BUDGET PHONE WITH A STYLUS</h3><p>This year’s 4G-only edition of the Moto G Stylus continues to offer the excellent balance of features and cost-saving measures as last year’s model. It’s a good phone for the price, whether you’re a stylus devotee or just want a big cheap phone, and it works on all three major US networks.</p><p>The Moto G Stylus has a big 6.8-inch 1080p LCD display, good battery life with its 5,000mAh cell, and ample internal storage with 128GB of capacity. With a capable MediaTek Helio G88 processor and a healthy 6GB of RAM, the G Stylus performs well with everyday tasks. The cameras, though flawed, are good enough to get by. You won’t find an amazing night mode or top-notch picture quality here, but for a sub-$300 phone, it does the job just fine. The G Stylus is missing an NFC chip for contactless payment, and it doesn’t have wireless charging or an IP rating for water resistance, which are all common omissions at this price.</p><p>The Moto G Stylus’ stylus lives in the device, like the one on the Galaxy S22 Ultra. Popping it out brings up a quick menu of shortcuts to stylus-friendly apps, like its coloring book app. It’s a feature set intended for a more casual user than the likes of the S22 Ultra and, as a result, feels more approachable.</p><p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?xcust=___vg__p_21184237__t_w__r_google.com__d_D&amp;id=66960X1514734&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https://www.motorola.com/us/smartphones-moto-g-stylus-gen-3/p?skuId=723&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-cheap\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/aFS7beG0cfwz9svfm_qcukNVhxE=/0x0:1000x1000/300x300/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 300w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eaDcfod7sRBqvJZvKbvLVFsW7lc=/0x0:1000x1000/400x400/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 400w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hzFx8P9Rd6f99Kp6CNNJWsCVu_Q=/0x0:1000x1000/500x500/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 500w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RZz2tnOjqoSYI_ND5NgSg8QLgf8=/0x0:1000x1000/600x600/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 600w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hRWdYkJgJSByj2Gi7XZ5aRbCsPY=/0x0:1000x1000/700x700/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 700w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/GBBfJ_EkifQxq3PfXPBsY8C1jds=/0x0:1000x1000/800x800/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 800w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/x3Bgp3uXMobq0of6cBhQ4i1XDcc=/0x0:1000x1000/900x900/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 900w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/abKgU6zeXoTNt_a11CQ9SMi3qII=/0x0:1000x1000/1000x1000/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 1000w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8xcMxdcW0RGCn9dH8KjqCaBnnpE=/0x0:1000x1000/1100x1100/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 1100w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/5eCruTIk9Th-x4FxZ5CR_5d1Plk=/0x0:1000x1000/1200x1200/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HtbtULTtV-9OH6Eg55fRh4QCDgg=/0x0:1000x1000/1300x1300/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23390220/ajohnson_220411_5138_0001_squ.jpg 1300w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/YIAXwptx2iIxwR4XBbT-9se5FWY=/0x0:1000x1000/1400x1400/filters:focal(500x500:501x501):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/2