0 counterparts by almost six times as much. Aided by a year of depreciation, it’s still probably one of the best handsets you can find for the asking price.\"<br>&nbsp;</p><p>\"And riding high on that success, the Huawei P30 Pro feels like an encore. The Huawei P30 Pro doubles down on the things that worked about its predecessor and pushes the envelope for smartphone photography even further. If you want the best smartphone camera on the market, you’ve found it.\"</p><p><a href=\"https://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/685609/samsung-galaxy-s21-vs-galaxy-s20-what-changed/\"><img src=\"https://www.idgcdn.com.au/dimg/120x120/dimg/galaxy-s21_plus_budspro_watch_lifestyle_violet.jpg\"></a> <strong>READ MORE</strong><a href=\"https://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/685609/samsung-galaxy-s21-vs-galaxy-s20-what-changed/\">Samsung Galaxy S21 vs Galaxy S20: What’s Changed</a></p><p><strong>You can </strong><a href=\"https://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/review/huawei/p30-pro/659344/?pp=1#cb\"><strong>read our full review of the Huawei P30 Pro here</strong></a><strong>.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><h3>Pros</h3><p>Glossy aesthetics</p><p>Quad-lens camera with zoom for days</p><ul><li>Works with Google apps</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/650745/which-smartphone-should-buy/\"><img src=\"https://www.idgcdn.com.au/dimg/120x120/dimg/screenshot_2018-10-20_iphone_xs_and_iphone_xs_max_bring_the_best_and_biggest_displays_to_iphone_2.png\"></a> <strong>READ MORE</strong><a href=\"https://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/650745/which-smartphone-should-buy/\">Which smartphone should I buy?</a></p><h3>Cons</h3><p>EMUI</p><ul><li>Custom memory expansion format</li></ul><h3>Where to buy?</h3><p>In Australia, you can find the Huawei P30 Pro through the following:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/671616/how-much-does-oppo-find-x2-pro-cost-australia/\"><img src=\"https://www.idgcdn.com.au/dimg/120x120/dimg/dsc_0798_dxo_2.jpg\"></a> <strong>READ MORE</strong><a 