(1, 3, 5, 'If you’re after the best iPhone Apple has ever made by a long way, then the iPhone 13 Pro Max is it - mostly down to having a genuinely long-lasting battery. You’ll need deep pockets, both literally and figuratively, to own this phone, as it’s big and rather expensive - but you’re getting a decent amount for your money.', 'Gareth Beavis', 'GarethBeavis@gmail.com', '2022-07-31 18:49:36', NULL),
(3, 50, 5, 'Good', 'Khanh', 'daohoangmykhanh@gmail.com', '2022-08-02 06:27:18', NULL);

